Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Emma Wilcox Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates the portion of state route 60 between Shumla Road and Lakeview Road in the town of Stockton, county of Chautauqua, as the "Emma Wilcox Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Emma Wilcox Memorial Highway"
